column1: TABLE 3.A SECTORAL BACKGROUND DATA FOR AGRICULTURE
Additional information  (only for those livestock types for which tier 2 was used) (a)
(a) See also tables 10A.1, 10A.2 and 10A.3 of volume 4 of the 2006 IPCC Guidelines. These data are relevant if Parties do not have data on average feed intake.
(b) Disaggregate to the split actually used. Add columns to the table if necessary.
(c) For cattle, buffalo and sheep specify feeding situation in accordance with table 10.5 of volume 4 of the 2006 IPCC Guidelines.
